#!/usr/bin/env retro

# Overview

Toki Pona is a very small constructed language. This is
a quick and dirty tool to provide a (very) rough translation
to English.

A couple of resources:

* http://tokipona.org
* http://tokipona.net/tp/janpije/index.php

